{"tid":2078930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然正常唔鬥黃, 但選舉就係鬥黃","createTime":"2020-06-25T11:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T12:07:16.000Z","uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e158571553f96a93dddfd99ca57e2e4da96ca45","tid":2078930,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"因為quota有限, 同日常唔同, 候選人要夠黃先好入議會做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以泛民, 尤其民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n素人都要夠黃先投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(例: 天水連線有人今日唔出席初選論壇, 因為去咗元朗yoho<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fCypfS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fCypfS</a><br />\n利申: 我港島, 無意為新西人拉票, 純議事論事)<br />\n<br />\n鐘意鬥黃嘅連登仔選舉中可以發揮鬥黃精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不過, 選完就告一段落, 唔好再鬥, 槍口一致對共</span></span><br />\n認同請推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔認同嘅, 歡迎討論點解「選舉都唔應該鬥黃」, 請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542c4c930da7d6edf4cfeb901860627d75b1080e","tid":2078930,"uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"唔鬥黃不如抽籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e733788ea8ca0d5caa8afcb3009adb2415cb5e5","tid":2078930,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542c4c930da7d6edf4cfeb901860627d75b1080e","tid":2078930,"uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"唔鬥黃不如抽籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"所以候選人要有張CV, 唔係唔知你有幾黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱晒連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}